We have two options how we can store assets positon/scale/rotation.
a) four points, each represents one corner
b) width, height + 3v3 matrix

Seems like matrix could simplify a lot of transformations but at the same time
UV coordinates would be to be stored somewhere as well.

Thats why for now we stick with storing assets as four points, each point is x,y,u,v.
For transformations like all scaling, rotations we are going to use matricies.
For transition is not useful since it's super easy to just add cursor position to points.